description: Returns a list of aliases for a flow.

parameters.name: flowIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the flow for which aliases are being returned.

nested_items.name: flowAliasSummaries
nested_items.description: A list, each member of which contains information about an alias.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the total number of results is greater than the maxResults value provided in the request, use this token when making another request in the nextToken field to return the next batch of results.
